module.exports = Object.assign(function GamepadButton () {}, {
	FACE_1: 0,
	FACE_2: 1,
	FACE_3: 2,
	FACE_4: 3,

	L_SHOULDER_1: 4,
	R_SHOULDER_1: 5,
	L_SHOULDER_2: 6,
	R_SHOULDER_2: 7,

	SELECT: 8,
	START: 9,

	DPAD_UP: 12,
	DPAD_DOWN: 13,
	DPAD_LEFT: 14,
	DPAD_RIGHT: 15,

	VENDOR: 16,
});
